    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just checked my last lab results from last month and my creatinine was only slightly elevated, nothing crazy. i don't really want to wait for an appointment just for a headache, it's driving me nuts. are you sure a small dose is okay? i feel like i can handle it if it's just a little bit of ibuprofen.",
